headline.main: Papua New Guinea Hit by 6.5 Earthquake, No Tsunami Expected
headline.print_headline: Papua New Guinea Hit by 6.5 Earthquake, No Tsunami Expected

lead_paragraph: Papua New Guinea was shaken by a magnitude 6.5 earthquake on Monday but no destructive tsunami was expected, officials said.
